  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shallot halves</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges</strong> and <strong>chopped pepper </strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-22 min or until the veg is tender and the pepper is slightly charred – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>to a bowl with<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>fennel seeds</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix thoroughly until fully combined, divide into 5 per person and roll into meatballs – these are your <strong>pork meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> and cook for an initial 4-5 min or until starting to brown all over</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>conchiglie</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>conchiglie</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>conchiglie</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once the veg is tender and slightly charred, add the <strong>roasted veg</strong> to the <strong>food processor</strong> with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!), your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[ 1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>Greek cheese &</strong> <strong>red pepper sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are browned, add the <strong>Greek cheese & red pepper sauce</strong> to the pan with 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and cook, covered, for 8-10 min further or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once cooked through, add the <strong>drained conchiglie </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix – these are your <strong>pork meatballs with Greek cheese & red pepper conchiglie</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-meatballs-with-greek-cheese-and-red-pepper-conchiglie/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pork meatballs with Greek cheese & red pepper conchiglie </strong>and crumble the <strong>remaining Greek cheese </strong>on top</p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
